comments.body:
***Note**: [Comment](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ARROW-4467?focusedCommentId=16812216) by Zhiyuan Zheng (zhiyuan.zheng):*
We should take the following steps:
1. Update `sqlparser-rs` to support `CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE` syntax;
1. Update sqlparser-rs version to 0.3.0+.
1. Create a repl for DataFusion;
1. Add a `Dockerfile`;

    I would like to resolve it if there is nobody working on this one.
